OL,3,CPlans put forward to suspend
OL,4,Cpolitician for third time in six months
OL,6,FA Jersey politician could be suspended
OL,7,Ffor the third time in just over six
OL,8,Fmonths, after his colleagues lodged
OL,9,Fanother proposal to temporarily remove
OL,10,Fhim from the States Assembly.
OL,12,FDeputy Philip Ozouf was sentenced to
OL,13,F120 hours of community service earlier
OL,14,Fthis month for employing five Rwandan
OL,15,Fnationals in his laundry business
OL,16,Fwithout the correct work permits.
