OL,3,CPlans put forward to suspend
OL,4,Cpolitician for third time in six months
OL,6,FOzouf, 55, first became a States
OL,7,FMember in 1999 and has previously held
OL,8,Fsenior government positions, including
OL,9,FExternal Relations Minister.
OL,11,FPressure has been growing on him to
OL,12,Fresign, including from the island's
OL,13,Fmost senior politician, Deputy Lyndon
OL,14,FFarnham, who told ITV News, "it would
OL,15,Fbe appropriate for Deputy Ozouf to
OL,16,Fconsider stepping down".
OL,18,FHowever, he has shown no sign of
OL,19,Fwishing to step back voluntarily.
